  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为零售场景设计一个状态机，涵盖从收银台启动到库存管理的完整流程。核心是从OFF状态开始，通过不同的START指令进入不同路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "START",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我看到有两个启动分支：一个是通过Retail_OrderManagement进入WARMUP，另一个是通过Retail_Inventory直接进入INIT。这两条路径的触发条件有什么区别？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。WARMUP路径需要MODE=WARM_UP参数，用于预热场景；INIT路径是标准库存初始化。WARMUP完成后温度达标会自动回到OFF，而INIT会进入预冷流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "MODE=WARM_UP",
        "warm reached"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出OFF到WARMUP和INIT的分支。INIT之后经过init_seconds进入PRECOOL，这个计时器命名我用init_seconds还是简写？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "init_seconds",
        "PRECOOL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用init_seconds elapsed作为条件。PRECOOL阶段要监控温度，当T5 <= TSP - precool_band时才能进入RUN状态。这里T5是实际温度，TSP是设定点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRECOOL",
        "RUN",
        "T5",
        "TSP",
        "precool_band"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。PRECOOL到RUN的温度条件我记下了。另外我注意到INIT和PRECOOL都可以直接到READY状态，这是通过ready flag true触发的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "PRECOOL",
        "READY",
        "ready flag true"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，READY是一个可中断的待命状态。实际上RUN状态在ready flag为true时也会转入READY。READY恢复时通过ready flag cleared回到RUN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RUN",
        "READY",
        "ready flag true",
        "ready flag cleared"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，READY和RUN之间有双向切换。我注意到这个设计里READY状态跟Retail_CouponSystem有关联，是优惠券系统需要这个待命状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Retail_CouponSystem可以发起HOLD指令让RUN进入暂停。另外Retail_CustomerLoyalty也能让READY进入HOLD。暂停后通过Retail_OrderManagement的RESUME恢复运行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HOLD",
        "RUN",
        "READY",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "RESUME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "HOLD的恢复路径我确认了。关于停止流程，STOP指令是由Retail_Inventory发起吗？还有OFF指令的来源是Retail_CouponSystem？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOP",
        "OFF",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，任意状态都可以通过这两个指令回到OFF。STOP或OFF指令生效后系统关闭。另外WARMUP完成后温度达标也会自动回到OFF。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "any",
        "STOP",
        "OFF",
        "warm reached"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我注意到安全方面还需要处理。如果Safety事件触发，INIT、PRECOOL、RUN、READY、HOLD、WARMUP都应该能进入安全关机流程。我设计一个SAFE_SHUTDOWN状态来统一处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safety",
        "SAFE_SHUTDOWN",
        "INIT",
        "PRECOOL",
        "RUN",
        "READY",
        "HOLD",
        "WARMUP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "很好，SAFE_SHUTDOWN是必要的。安全关机后需要RESET操作才能回到OFF，而且RESET必须来自Retail_OrderManagement并且等于ACK_ALARM确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SAFE_SHUTDOWN",
        "RESET",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "ACK_ALARM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "SAFE_SHUTDOWN到OFF的条件我记为RESET(Retail_OrderManagement)=ACK_ALARM。让我整体检查一下：从Retail_PointOfSale开始的OFF状态，两条启动路径，温度控制流程，READY待命，HOLD暂停机制，以及安全关机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "OFF",
        "SAFE_SHUTDOWN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，WARMUP到OFF的条件我写的是warm reached，但之前说的是温度达标。需要确认这个表述是否准确，还是应该用warmup completed？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "OFF",
        "warm reached"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我核对一下，您原文说的是warm reached，这可以理解为预热目标达成。如果改成warmup completed可能更清晰，但保持warm reached也可以。您确认用哪个？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
